original_title: Built to Spill: Hi, How Are You - Live at the Moody Theater
overview: Built to Spill plays a special, 4-song set at the Hi, How Are You Project benefit, a foundation set up in memory of Daniel Johnston to end the stigma around Mental Health conversations. Filmed live at the Moody Theater in Austin Texas in 2019.
title: Built to Spill: Hi, How Are You - Live at the Moody Theater
